snippet.title: Star Realms Deckbuilding Game | Claim Your Star Realm
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD FREE at http://StarRealms.com/digital-game/

The Star Realms digital app is now available, letting users enjoy the authentic Star Realms experience on their mobile devices and home computers. The game features a variety of ways to play, including an immersive single-player campaign mode, thrilling battles against three different levels of A.I., and most excitingly, a robust online multiplayer mode!
